1. Trump: Big news will be announced at 10 o'clock tonight;
2. Fed Powell: In some cases, it is appropriate to cut interest rates this year;
3. Powell: Trump's call for rate cuts will not affect the Fed;
4. Mikami Yua's Meme coin Mikami was released in the early morning, and it has fallen more than 80% from its high point;
5. The U.S. Treasury Department will hold several crypto industry roundtables next week;
6. DeFi Development approved a 1-for-7 stock split and continued to bet on Solana;
7. Former SafeMoon CEO denied the allegations and accused the founder on the first day of trial;
8. The U.S. OCC confirmed that banks can buy and sell custodial crypto assets and outsource related services based on customer instructions;
9. Arizona signed HB 2749 to establish the first cryptocurrency reserve.
